01:39:21,005 --> 01:39:22,305
<font color="#ffff00">o porão.</font>

1414
01:39:23,199 --> 01:39:24,554
<font color="#ffff00">Ki-woo...</font>

1415
01:39:25,555 --> 01:39:28,621
<font color="#ffff00">você sabe que tipo de plano
