1432
01:40:29,299 --> 01:40:30,666
<font color="#ffff00">Pai...</font>

1433
01:40:32,701 --> 01:40:34,294
<font color="#ffff00">eu sinto muito.</font>

1434
01:40:34,912 --> 01:40:36,454
<font color="#ffff00">Pelo quê?</font>

1435
01:40:39,648 --> 01:40:40,981
<font color="#ffff00">Tudo.</font>

1436
01:40:42,087 --> 01:40:43,687
<font color="#ffff00">Tudo isso.</font>

1437
01:40:45,924 --> 01:40:47,625
<font color="#ffff00">Eu vou cuidar de tudo.</font>

1438
01:40:48,760 --> 01:40:50,578
<font color="#ffff00">Do que está falando?</font>

1439
01:40:53,014 --> 01:40:55,607
<font color="#ffff00">Por que está abraçando
essa pedra?</font>

1440
01:40:56,326 --> 01:40:57,743
<font color="#ffff00">Isso?</font>

1441
01:41:03,483 --> 01:41:06,218
<font color="#ffff00">Ela fica sempre
atrás de mim.</font>

1442
01:41:08,656 --> 01:41:09,977
<font color="#ffff00">Eu acho...</font>

1443
01:41:10,678 --> 01:41:12,742
<font color="#ffff00">que precisa dormir um pouco.</font>

